reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It lasted two years, and was a great value
reviews.reviewText: This case was pretty and took a lot of abuse. It still looked nice after two years, but I cracked the outer case so the credit card holder didn't work anymore. It really protected my phone from scratches and internal damage. I just bought another one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love the card holder feature, lightweight but sturdy case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It fits my phone great. I have dropped my phone and my screen was protectedfrom the edges being raised.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Definitely would recommend
reviews.reviewText: The case definitely doesn't FEEL like the nicest thing but it does the job well. I dropped my phone several times, once from about 4 ft high, straight onto bathroom tile. I thought for sure my phone was going to be wrecked. Not even a scratch on the screen. The card holder works perfectly fine still.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Too small for more than 1 card
reviews.reviewText: Really cute product but its only holds 1 card when I usually always carry my ID and a bank card. It won't close so makes it not as sturdy. But overall cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Broke the 1st day
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for my S21. The rubber shell didn't fit properly, then the outer casing broke as I was trying to put it on. I loved the color and concept, but some improvements need to be made on quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 6, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this thing!
reviews.reviewText: I leave home with just my phone and keys all the time now! I don't lose my license or worry about breaking my card in my pocket anymore and it's protected my phone thru 3 drops so far. It's a little slick when you set it down so it will slide off counters if you're not careful (which I found out I'm not) but it takes a fall really well. It holds 2 cards with no trouble and you can squeeze a 3rd in there but it doesn't close quite right. It does block the tap feature so I just carry 2 to keep it easy to open. This might be my favorite purchase this year.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 1.5+ yrs, takes drops like a champ
reviews.reviewText: Klutz here. Have dropped my poor phone SO. MANY. TIMES. It's still in one piece, and perfectly survived my abuse! The case has fallen, and _hard_. The little wallet door has even popped out w/ cards falling out. It gets put back together easy peasy (wallet still functions). No glue/etc. Have tucked vax card/hidden emergency cash between the layers and still solid. Re-buying after last tumble was too much of a doozy and after this long I'm happy to reinvest. I keep 3 cards in it always, 2-3 works but 4 would absolutely not.Friend & Apple store employee told me the most protective are hard outside with rubber for shock absorption inside, and can attest it works.Edit to add: works perfectly with pop sockets.
Produto bom, atende as expectativas, vendedor atencioso e com boa comunicação.
Agora coloco os cartões mais necessários, e não saio mais com carteira. O material é bom e encaixa perfeitamente!

reviews.reviewTitle: Muito grande, material péssimo, película atrapalha touch e digital
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Pelo preço, eu esperava que a qualidade fosse imensamente superior. Dá pra ver que em 5 dias de uso a parte traseira da capinha vai se desgastar e mudar de cor, material de baixissima qualidade, frágil. É extremamente grande, da muito volume pro celular e a película impede o uso da digital como forma de bloqueio. Péssimo, me arrependo mto da compra. Nem vou usar.
